 id="iigoyv-2" class="gjs-plg-flex-column"><h3 id="iwhy1title-4">Flexible payment methods</h3><span id="iwhy1text-4"><ul><li>Crypto</li><li>Paypal</li><li id="i4uyrq">Buy now pay later options</li></ul></span></div></div><div data-type-role="flex-row" id="iodw11-2" class="gjs-plg-flex-row"><div data-type-role="flex-column" id="ijlypi-2" class="gjs-plg-flex-column"><div data-type-icon="" id="ifoi2o-2" class="gjs-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="currentColor" d="M18.577 6.183a1 1 0 0 1 .24 1.394l-5.666 8.02c-.36.508-.665.94-.94 1.269c-.287.34-.61.658-1.038.86a2.83 2.83 0 0 1-2.03.153c-.456-.137-.82-.406-1.149-.702c-.315-.285-.672-.668-1.09-1.116l-1.635-1.753a1 1 0 1 1 1.462-1.364l1.606 1.722c.455.487.754.806.998 1.027c.24.216.344.259.385.271c.196.06.405.045.598-.046c.046-.022.149-.085.36-.338c.216-.257.473-.62.863-1.171l5.642-7.986a1 1 0 0 1 1.394-.24"></path></svg></div></div><div data-type-role="flex-column" id="iox06f-2" class="gjs-plg-flex-column"><h3 id="iwhy1title-3-2">Reasonable price</h3><span id="iwhy1text-3-2">All Parts in the builds are economically sourced to create a reasonably priced product</span></div></div><div data-type-role="flex-row" id="izbi96-2" class="gjs-plg-flex-row"><div data-type-role="flex-column" id="i1n1l2-2" class="gjs-plg-flex-column"><div data-type-icon="" id="i2b6m6-3" class="gjs-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="currentColor" d="M18.577 6.183a1 1 0 0 1 .24 1.394l-5.666 8.02c-.36.508-.665.94-.94 1.269c-.287.34-.61.658-1.038.86a2.83 2.83 0 0 1-2.03.153c-.456-.137-.82-.406-1.149-.702c-.315-.285-.672-.668-1.09-1.116l-1.635-1.753a1 1 0 1 1 1.462-1.364l1.606 1.722c.455.487.754.806.998 1.027c.24.216.344.259.385.271c.196.06.405.045.598-.046c.046-.022.149-.085.36-.338c.216-.257.473-.62.863-1.171l5.642-7.986a1 1 0 0 1 1.394-.24"></path></svg></div></div><div data-type-role="flex-column" id="irwqxu-2" class="gjs-plg-flex-column"><h3 id="iwhy1title-2-3">Fast Shiping</h3><span id="iwhy1text-2-3">All orders are usually shipped within a week</span></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="i83pzu" class="gjs-section"><div id="i3i89z" class="gjs-container"><section id="gpc-info-section" class="gjs-section"><div class="gjs-container"><article id="gpc-info"><header class="gpc-head"><div class="gpc-label"><span class="gpc-icon-wrap"><img src="https://api.iconify.design/mdi:book-open-variant.svg?color=currentColor&amp;width=22&amp;height=22" alt="Guide icon"/></span><span class="gpc-label-text">Buying Guide</span></div><h2 class="gjs-t-h1 gpc-title">Find Your Perfect Gaming PC with Sovereign Tech</h2><p class="gpc-lead">Where independent performance meets real value. We focus on the right components, smart configurations, and systems built to perform without compromise.</p><div class="gpc-cta"><a href="./build.html" class="gjs-link-box gjs-t-button gpc-btn"><span>Build Your PC</span></a><a href="./order.html" class="gjs-link-box gpc-btn gpc-btn--ghost"><span>Order a Prebuilt</span></a></div></header><figure class="gpc-figure"><img src="https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=gaming%20pc%20setup&amp;w=1200&amp;h=540" alt="Sleek gaming PC setup on a desk" loading="lazy"/></figure><div class="gpc-divider"></div><section class="gpc-section"><h3 class="gpc-h3">Introduction</h3><p>Choosing a gaming PC is about more than raw power — it’s about balance. Performance, cost, reliability, and future upgrades all matter. At Sovereign Tech, we remove the noise and focus on what actually makes a difference.</p><p>Whether you’re chasing smooth esports gameplay or immersive AAA experiences, we align your budget and priorities with the right gaming PC — built fast, shipped quickly, and priced honestly.</p></section><section class="gpc-section"><h3 class="gpc-h3">What Matters Most</h3><ul class="gpc-list"><li>Systems are available as fully assembled, ready‑to‑play PCs or highly configurable builds designed for long‑term upgradeability.</li><li>Core performance is driven by your CPU (Intel Core or AMD Ryzen), GPU (NVIDIA GeForce RTX or AMD Radeon), sufficient RAM, and fast storage — SSDs strongly preferred over HDDs.</li><li>Modern features like ray tracing, AI upscaling, and frame generation are now accessible from entry‑level to high‑end systems.</li><li>From affordable starter builds to enthusiast machines, we focus on performance per dollar, smart part selection, and future‑proof design.</li></ul></section><section class="gpc-section"><h3 class="gpc-h3">Discover Your Ideal Gaming PC</h3><p>Build or configure your gaming PC with Sovereign Tech and experience systems designed to look sharp, run cool, and perform consistently.</p><p>The market can feel overwhelming. Small differences in components can have a big impact on performance, lifespan, and upgrade potential. We bring clarity — helping you choose a system that fits your needs now and later.</p><p>The best gaming PC isn’t defined by a single component. It’s the result of understanding trade‑offs and choosing what aligns with how you actually play.</p></section><section class="gpc-section gpc-grid-2"><article class="gpc-card"><div class="gpc-card-head"><img src="https://api.iconify.design/mdi:desktop-classic.svg?color=currentColor&amp;width=24&amp;height=24" alt="Prebuilt PC icon"/><h4 class="gpc-h4">Prebuilt Gaming PCs</h4></div><p>If you value convenience, reliability, and strong value, prebuilts are excellent. We offer Intel Core (i3–i9) and AMD Ryzen (3–9) systems paired with balanced graphics options.</p><ul class="gpc-list"><li>Professionally assembled, tested, and covered by warranty.</li><li>Predictable performance and time savings vs. building from scratch.</li><li>Select preconfigured systems meet common budget/performance targets.</li><li>Windows 11 Home installed and activated.</li></ul></article><article class="gpc-card"><div class="gpc-card-head"><img src="https://api.iconify.design/mdi:toolbox.svg?color=currentColor&amp;width=24&amp;height=24" alt="Custom PC icon"/><h4 class="gpc-h4">Custom Gaming PCs</h4></div><p>For full control and flexibility. Choose your motherboard, CPU, memory, storage, PSU, cooling, and case — step by step.</p><ul class="gpc-list"><li>Tailored performance, aesthetics, and upgrade paths.</li><li>Ideal for specific targets or unique workloads.</li><li>Expert support for newcomers and enthusiasts alike.</li></ul></article></section><section class="gpc-section gpc-grid-2"><article class="gpc-card"><div class="gpc-card-head"><img src="https://api.iconify.design/mdi:laptop.svg?color=currentColor&amp;width=24&amp;height=24" alt="Laptop icon"/><h4 class="gpc-h4">Gaming Laptops vs Desktop PCs</h4></div><p>Desktops typically deliver higher performance, better cooling, greater value, and easier upgrades.</p><ul class="gpc-list"><li>Laptops offer portability with trade‑offs in thermals and upgradeability.</li><li>Mid‑range laptops: ~3–4 years competitive; high‑end up to ~6.</li><li>Desktops last longer thanks to modular components and superior cooling.</li></ul></article><article class="gpc-card"><div class="gpc-card-head"><img src="https://api.iconify.design/mdi:lightning-bolt.svg?color=currentColor&amp;width=24&amp;height=24" alt="Core components icon"/><h4 class="gpc-h4">Core Components of a High‑Performance PC</h4></div><h5 class="gpc-h5">Graphics Card &amp; Processor</h5><ul class="gpc-list"><li>GPUs drive rendering, effects, and frame rates; dedicated GPUs far outperform integrated graphics.</li><li>CPUs handle logic, physics, AI, and background tasks; core count, clocks, and architecture matter.</li></ul><h5 class="gpc-h5">Intel Core vs AMD Ryzen</h5><ul class="gpc-list"><li>Intel: higher single‑core speeds in some titles.</li><li>AMD: more cores and strong multitasking efficiency.</li><li>AMD often more power‑efficient and competitively priced.</li></ul><h5 class="gpc-h5">AMD Radeon vs NVIDIA GeForce</h5><ul class="gpc-list"><li>NVIDIA leads in high‑end performance and features like RTX/DLSS.</li><li>AMD emphasizes value with competitive performance per dollar.</li></ul><h5 class="gpc-h5">Storage: SSDs and HDDs</h5><ul class="gpc-list"><li>SSDs: rapid boot and near‑instant load times.</li><li>HDDs: larger capacity at lower cost but slower performance.</li><li>Recommend SSD with at least 1TB total storage for most players.</li></ul></article></section><section class="gpc-section"><h3 class="gpc-h3">Budget Gaming PCs: Performance Without Overspending</h3><p>High performance doesn’t require a premium price tag. Well‑balanced budget PCs handle esports smoothly and run modern games at sensible settings. We maximize performance per dollar without sacrificing reliability.</p><div class="gpc-card gpc-stacked"><div class="gpc-card-head"><img src="https://api.iconify.design/mdi:format-list-numbered.svg?color=currentColor&amp;width=22&amp;height=22" alt="Priority list icon"/><h4 class="gpc-h4">Getting the Most Value: Priority Order</h4></div><ol class="gpc-olist"><li>CPU</li><li>GPU</li><li>RAM</li><li>SSD</li><li>Motherboard</li><li>Power supply</li><li>Case and cooling</li></ol><p class="gpc-note">Boost value further by tuning settings, enabling Windows performance modes, keeping drivers updated, and watching for sales.</p></div></section><section class="gpc-section gpc-grid-2"><article class="gpc-card"><div class="gpc-card-head"><img src="https://api.iconify.design/mdi:monitor.svg?color=currentColor&amp;width=22&amp;height=22" alt="Monitor icon"/><h4 class="gpc-h4">Accessories &amp; Peripherals</h4></div><ul class="gpc-list"><li><strong>Monitors:</strong> Higher refresh = smoother motion; resolution affects performance; low input lag matters for competitive play.</li><li><strong>Keyboards &amp; Mice:</strong> Mechanical keyboards for precision and durability; adjustable DPI mice for control.</li><li><strong>Audio &amp; Streaming:</strong> Quality audio improves immersion and awareness; low‑latency sound helps directional cues.</li></ul></article><article class="gpc-card"><div class="gpc-card-head"><img src="https://api.iconify.design/mdi:progress-wrench.svg?color=currentColor&amp;width=22&amp;height=22" alt="Maintenance icon"/><h4 class="gpc-h4">Maintaining &amp; Upgrading</h4></div><ul class="gpc-list"><li>Clean dust every 3–6 months and maintain proper airflow.</li><li>Replace thermal paste when necessary.</li><li>Good cable management improves cooling and upgradeability.</li></ul><p><strong>Upgrading over time:</strong> RAM, SSDs, and GPUs are common. CPU/GPU upgrades dramatically impact frame rates and responsiveness.</p></article></section><section class="gpc-section"><h3 class="gpc-h3">Final Thoughts</h3><p>The right gaming PC fits your needs, budget, and future plans. From components to peripherals and maintenance, thoughtful choices make a measurable difference in performance and longevity. Sovereign Tech stands for independent design, smart performance, and systems built to last.</p></section><section class="gpc-section"><h3 class="gpc-h3">Frequently Asked Questions</h3><div class="gpc-faq"><details><summary><img src="https://api.iconify.design/mdi:help-circle-outline.svg?color=currentColor&amp;width=20&amp;height=20" alt="Question icon"/>
              What PC is best for gaming?
            </summary><p>A modern CPU paired with a capable GPU — for example, a Ryzen 7 or Core i9 with an RTX‑class graphics card — delivers excellent gaming performance.</p></details><details><summary><img src="https://api.iconify.design/mdi:cash.svg?color=currentColor&amp;width=20&amp;height=20" alt="Cost icon"/>
              How much does a gaming PC cost in Australia?
            </summary><p>Entry‑level systems typically start around $1,000, while strong 1080p–1440p builds usually fall between $1,300 and $2,000.</p></details><details><summary><img src="https://api.iconify.design/mdi:check-decagram.svg?color=currentColor&amp;width=20&amp;height=20" alt="Prebuilt icon"/>
              Why choose a prebuilt PC?
            </summary><p>Prebuilt systems offer warranties, professional assembly, and predictable performance at competitive prices.</p></details><details><summary><img src="https://api.iconify.design/mdi:tools.svg?color=currentColor&amp;width=20&amp;height=20" alt="Custom build icon"/>
              Why build a custom PC?
